text: Barton Hall is field house on the campus of Cornell University, USA Barton Hall may also refer to most notable buildings: *Barton Hall (Alabama), plantation house near Cherokee, Alabama, USA *RAF Barton Hall, former RAF station and country house in the parish of Barton, Preston, England *Barton Hall, a country house in the parish of Barton Turf, Norfolk Category:Architectural disambiguation pages
